{"tid":811050,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女友辛酸史，慘L過做兵","createTime":"2018-09-08T13:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T14:26:56.000Z","uid":203423,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea28b34d32bb6a7a3fc1c5a260b7969c13a91dc3","tid":811050,"uid":203423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"話說拍拖3個月都唔夠，已經好似拍咗幾年咁，見都唔見得多，最多係接佢收工行翻屋企，依家大家都翻緊學(唔係中學)，所以其實有好多時間見，但係佢就瘋狂返工，我就自己一個on99咁係屋企，等佢收工去接佢。<br />\n<br />\n重點泥啦！！！！我同佢見已經唔多，佢仲要有時間同啲fd過，都唔同我過，同性都唔緊要，係異性，係異性，係異性！！！我約佢食早餐，午餐，晚餐，總係有嘢做，人地一約就去，我有同佢講過，佢話好早識，仲要係gay嘅，叫我唔使擔心，話feel到對佢有意思男人已經保持左距離，我屌，係男人都嬲啦，同我講無事，帽事都就泥啦。<br />\n<br />\n就算A1，話唔識拍拖都唔會拍緊拖嗰時，同異性朋友單獨出街啦。所以我希望天下所有gay佬全撚部死曬。<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下，點做！！！"},{"pid":"1b5511432a7914f930bb0d8f52758eb2e84b8ee8","tid":811050,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"c0a7f0c16fe35a7c2d3878d9255ae2756d369069","tid":811050,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3caf4ddc3b8c88a75